class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好變招fd post 統討論only</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你就咪撚係到呻拉<br />\n出面十九幾個post都講條仔幾衰幾賤，個個都知留言叫分手，D港女就博嘴有感覺架，我好愛佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d4da324ddf19e5c1e7440677ad868ade0604da","tid":327773,"uid":102306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"28歲人工13k, 仲唔走？"},{"pid":"36a254ede02195cbc871d6d046a4ac7986430ff9","tid":327773,"uid":14543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"好肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e9f19135e454476fb941342671d2576bcb81440","tid":327773,"uid":116113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"飛咗佢啦 咁小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地出街食2個人$150都話貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經係一人畀一次喎<br />\n<br />\n最難聽係句「我要食窮你」<br />\n如果係鍾意你，點會下下捨得你破費呀？<br />\n<br />\n樓主你而家都頂佢唔順<br />\n襯後生斬纜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c36f052bd4d79a46b37cf064f7224a07264c2c","tid":327773,"uid":1731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"以前同d女朋友都會互相整下嘢食當交換禮物<br />\n情人節佢整朱古力我整個蛋糕跟住一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3595119f9aab5cc5b082501dda88b9f9be3a8b11","tid":327773,"uid":111166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"飛左佢啦 做男人小家都咁真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49cce95990c6128f33db12ccc50744bf88078d4","tid":327773,"uid":2097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:34:00.000Z","msg":"錢都唔肯為你洗下嘅愛極都有限啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so